songs.title: Sensitive
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh
Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh

[Verse 1: Ally, Dinah]
Do you have a moment? Boy we need to talk
It’s a conversation that's been coming on, oh
Why you want me living like I’m in a cage?
I'm just tired of hoping that you're gonna change, oh

[Pre-Chorus: Ally, Normani]
I’m just out here baby living my life (my life, my life, my life)
I just have to say you got no right

[Chorus: Ally + Dinah]
You're so sensitive baby
And I love it about you
But you’re driving me crazy
‘Cause you're jealous in love
You're so sensitive baby
And I don’t wanna hurt you but I’m moving on
Yeah I’m moving on

Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh
Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh

[Verse 2: Camila, Lauren]
Oh baby
Boy you better man up, go and dry your tears
Don’t know where I’m going but I can’t stay here
You can find a new love, she can be the kind
That'll let you keep her right there by your side

[Pre-Chorus: Ally, Normani]
I’m just out here baby living my life (my life, my life, my life)
I just have to say you got no right (got no right)

[Chorus: Ally + Dinah,  Normani]
You're so sensitive baby (You're so sensitive)
And I love it about you (and I love it about you)
But you’re driving me crazy
‘Cause you're jealous in love ('Cause you're jealous in love)
You're so sensitive baby
And I don’t wanna hurt you but I’m moving on
Yeah I’m moving on

[Bridge: Lauren]
No question, you complete me
But two empty halves make for one empty hole
In the pit of my stomach and in the pit of my soul

[Pre-Chorus: All, Lauren, Normani]
I’m just out here baby living my life (my life, my life, my life)
I just have to say you got no right

[Chorus: Ally + Dinah, Lauren, Ally]
You're so sensitive baby
And I love it about you (and I love it about you)
But you’re driving me crazy
‘Cause you're jealous in love (jealous in love)
You're so sensitive baby
And I don’t wanna hurt you but I’m moving on
Yeah I’m moving on (I'm moving on)
You're so sensitive baby
And I love it about you
But you’re driving me crazy (you're driving me, you're driving me)
‘Cause you're jealous in love
You're so sensitive baby (so sensitive, ooh)
And I don’t wanna hurt you but I’m moving on
Yeah I’m moving on

[Outro - All, Ally, Lauren]
Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh (movin' on)
Oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh, oh
Baby I'm movin'...
